snippet.title: Tales of Luminaria - Trailer "ANSWER"
snippet.description:
An epic Tale that unfolds from 21 different points of view.
The newest mobile game in the Tales of series is here! for iOS / Android.
Our theme songs are created by Frederic and Keina Suda!

Follow us on:
Official website: https://luminaria-en.tales-ch.jp/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/to_luminaria_en
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Tales.of.Lum...
